                    <h2 data-uuid="52b17d697eae46bdb186b944c337acbf">Ptolemy’s World Map, 1482</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="c854620148e84e4e88d23ec94c8db888">This German map was based on a map that Ptolemy drew in the second century. Ptolemy only shows three continents: Europe, Africa, and Asia. This represents how Europeans understood the world before Columbus’ 1492 voyage.</p>
                </div>
